org.hps.analysis.util

Class HodoscopeChannelConditionsUtility

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.analysis.util.HodoscopeChannelConditionsUtility

  • public class HodoscopeChannelConditionsUtility
extends Object
    HodoscopeChannelConditionsUtility is a utility method designed to print out all of the conditions related to the hodoscope subdetector for a given run number and detector name.

    It may be run using the command: java -cp $HPS_JAVA org.hps.analysis.util.HodoscopeChannelConditionsUtility -R $RUN_NUMBER -d $HODOSCOPE_DETECTOR_NAME
